        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1863-11-17T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1863-11-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="5" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d5">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Koerner</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 57.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1863-11-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 17, 1863</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi>Your despatches, No. 57, of the 8th of October,
                    and No. 58, of the 11th of October, have been received. The facts they
                    communicate touching the efforts of the French emperor to increase his influence
                    in Spain, and on the subject of the insurrection in Santa Domingo, are very
                    interesting.</p>
                <p>You were quite right in assuring the Marquis of Miraflores that the accusations
                    to which you allude, concerning our participation in the troubles at Santa
                    Domingo, were utterly groundless. All reports or intimations of any kind that
                    the government or people of the United States have practiced, or are practicing,
                    interference in that quarter, or in Cuba, or elsewhere, are entirely without any
                    foundation in fact.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gustavus Koerner</hi>, Esq., &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>., &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>., &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>., <hi rend="italic">Madrid.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
